TITLE: Configuring Telerik UI for .NET MAUI in MauiProgram.cs
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to configure a .NET MAUI project to use Telerik UI controls. It shows how to add the Telerik namespace, register the controls, and call the UseTelerik extension method in the MauiProgram.cs file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/get-started/quickstart.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
using Telerik.Maui.Controls.Compatibility;

public static class MauiProgram
{
    public static MauiApp CreateMauiApp()
    {
        var builder = MauiApp.CreateBuilder();
        builder
            .UseMauiApp<App>()
            .UseTelerik()
            .ConfigureFonts(fonts =>
            {
                fonts.AddFont("OpenSans-Regular.ttf", "OpenSansRegular");
            });

        return builder.Build();
    }
}
```

