TITLE: Implementing Custom Sorting and Grouping Logic in MAUI DataGrid - C#
DESCRIPTION: This C# code snippet defines a custom column class 'CustomComboBoxColumn' that overrides methods to implement custom sorting and grouping logic using DelegateSortDescriptor and DelegateGroupDescriptor classes. The custom implementations ensure that the DataGrid maintains built-in UI features while applying specific sorting and grouping logic.
