TITLE: Handling Cell Selection in DataGrid for MAUI
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to handle cell selection within a RadDataGrid in a MAUI application. It listens for the SelectionChanged event and toggles the visibility of row details by adding or removing the selected cell's item from the ExpandedRowDetails collection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/knowledge-base/datagrid-maui-toggle-row-details-cell-selection.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
void dataGrid_SelectionChanged(System.Object sender, DataGridSelectionChangedEventArgs e)
{
    RadDataGrid dataGrid = sender as RadDataGrid;

    foreach (DataGridCellInfo item in e.AddedItems)
    {
        dataGrid.ExpandedRowDetails.Add(item.Item);
    }
    foreach (DataGridCellInfo item in e.RemovedItems)
    {
        dataGrid.ExpandedRowDetails.Remove(item.Item);
    }
}
```

