TITLE: Handling Cell Swipe Completion in C#
DESCRIPTION: Configures the action to be taken when a user completes a swipe gesture, modifying or removing the data item based on swipe direction and length.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/controls/listview/gestures/cell-swipe.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
private void listView_ItemSwipeCompleted(object sender, Telerik.Maui.Controls.ListView.ItemSwipeCompletedEventArgs e)
{
    var listView = (Telerik.Maui.Controls.RadListView)sender;
    var item = (Item)e.Item;

    if (e.Offset < 0)
    {
        if (Math.Abs(e.Offset) > this.listView.SwipeThreshold)
        {
            this.VM.Source.Remove(item);
        }
    }
    else
    {
        if (Math.Abs(e.Offset) > this.listView.SwipeThreshold)
        {
            item.Name = "Updated " + item.Name;
        }
    }

    listView.EndItemSwipe();
}
```

