TITLE: Defining Implicit Styles for Telerik MAUI Input Controls
DESCRIPTION: XAML styles that can be applied to RadTextInput, RadAutoComplete, RadEntry and RadComboBox controls. The styles include visual state management for different states (Normal, Focused, MouseOver) and properties for colors, borders, and text formatting.
