TITLE: Implementing CellContentStyleSelector in C#
DESCRIPTION: C# code snippet showing the implementation of MyCellContentStyleSelector class that derives from DataGridStyleSelector.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/controls/datagrid/theming-and-styles/style-selectors.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
public class MyCellContentStyleSelector : DataGridStyleSelector
{
    protected override DataGridStyle SelectStyle(object item, BindableObject container)
    {
        var dataItem = item as Data;
        var style = new DataGridStyle();

        if (dataItem.Salary < 55000)
        {
            style.TextColor = Colors.Red;
        }
        else
        {
            style.TextColor = Colors.Green;
        }

        return style;
    }
}
```

