TITLE: ViewModel for CollectionView Integration - C#
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines a `ViewModel` class that manages a collection of `Book` objects for the CollectionView. It includes a `Boolean IsLoading` property to control the BusyIndicator's state and a `LoadData` command for fetching data asynchronously.
