TITLE: Creating Custom Appointment Class in C#
DESCRIPTION: Defines a custom appointment class that inherits from Appointment and adds a Token property. Includes overrides for Copy and CopyFrom methods to handle the custom property during internal operations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/knowledge-base/custom-appointment-scheduler-net-maui.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
public class MyCustomAppointment : Appointment
{
    private string token;

    public string Token
    {
        get => this.token;
        set => this.UpdateValue(ref this.token, value);
    }

    public override IAppointment Copy()
    {
        var myAppt = new MyCustomAppointment();
        myAppt.CopyFrom(this);
        return myAppt;
    }

    public override void CopyFrom(IAppointment other)
    {
        var myAppt = other as MyCustomAppointment;
        if (myAppt != null)
        {
            this.Token = myAppt.Token;
        }

        base.CopyFrom(other);
    }
}
```

