TITLE: Implementing Custom StyleSelector Class in C#
DESCRIPTION: Creates a LocationStyleSelector class that inherits from IStyleSelector and selects styles based on the location type (Country or City).
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/controls/treeview/styling/itemstyle-selector.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
public class LocationStyleSelector : IStyleSelector
{
    public Style CountryStyle { get; set; }

    public Style CityStyle { get; set; }

    public Style SelectStyle(object item, BindableObject container)
    {
        var treeViewItem = item as TreeViewDataItem;
        if (treeViewItem == null)
        {
            return null;
        }

        var location = treeViewItem.Content;

        if (location is Country)
        {
            return this.CountryStyle;
        }
        else if (location is City)
        {
            return this.CityStyle;
        }

        return null;
    }
}
```

