TITLE: Implementing Native Chart Customization in C#
DESCRIPTION: Handles platform-specific chart customization through the HandlerChanged event to adjust vertical axis label positioning on iOS.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/knowledge-base/chart-vertical-axis-label-position-line-visibility.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

