TITLE: Implementing Custom String Converter for RangeSlider Labels in C#
DESCRIPTION: Defines a dictionary-based string converter to replace numeric values with meaningful names for RangeSlider labels.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/controls/rangeslider/labels.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
public class DictionaryStringConverter : IStringConverter
{
    private readonly Dictionary<double, string> valueToStringMap = new Dictionary<double, string>
    {
        { 0, "Very Cold" },
        { 25, "Cold" },
        { 50, "Medium" },
        { 75, "Hot" },
        { 100, "Very Hot" }
    };

    public string ConvertToString(double value)
    {
        if (this.valueToStringMap.TryGetValue(value, out string result))
        {
            return result;
        }
        return value.ToString();
    }
}
```

