TITLE: Registering Telerik Controls in MauiProgram.cs
DESCRIPTION: Registers the Telerik controls using the UseTelerik extension method in the MauiProgram.cs file. This is a necessary step to enable Telerik controls compatibility within the .NET MAUI project. The method configures font settings and integrates Telerik controls.
