TITLE: Registering Telerik UI for .NET MAUI Controls
DESCRIPTION: Register Telerik controls using the UseTelerik() method in the CreateMauiApp method of MauiProgram.cs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/migrate-to-net-maui.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
public static class MauiProgram
{
	public static MauiApp CreateMauiApp()
	{
		var builder = MauiApp.CreateBuilder();
		builder
			.UseTelerik()
			.UseMauiApp<App>()
			.ConfigureFonts(fonts =>
			{
				fonts.AddFont("OpenSans-Regular.ttf", "OpenSansRegular");
			});

		return builder.Build();
	}
}
```

