TITLE: Hiding Keyboard by Tapping Outside Entry Control in XAML
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to set the HideSoftInputOnTapped property on a ContentPage to automatically dismiss the soft keyboard when tapping outside an Entry control
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/maui-docs/blob/master/knowledge-base/hide-softkeyboard-without-losing-focus-maui-entry.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

